about: CowParade bronze casting was a gift commemorating the CowParade that commenced its international exhibition in Chicago in 1999. The gift was made in 2001. It is on display outside the Chicago Cultural Center in the Chicago Landmark Historic Michigan Boulevard District at the corner of Michigan Avenue and Washington Street in the Loop community area of Chicago, Illinois.
